    <td id="maintext"><!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="intro" -->
      <div id="cptitle">Make a Gift - Support Cal</div>
      <!-- closing div for id="cptitle" -->
      <p class="intro">Give a gift, write a letter, hire a student, attend 
        an event &#8212; however you do it, get involved at Berkeley.</p>
      <!-- InstanceEndEditable --><!-- InstanceBeginEditable name="hilite" --> 
      <div class="hilite">
        <p>The Cal Parents Fund<br>
        <span class="smallbody">Every year, Cal parents are invited to make a gift to The Cal Parents Fund to ensure ongoing excellence of a Berkeley education. State funding and tuition cover only a small portion of Berkeley's budget. As a result, parent gifts are essential to help preserve important undergraduate programs and opportunities that would not otherwise be possible.</span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody">During our 2011-12 campaign, 4,100 Berkeley families contributed $1,909,053 to The Cal Parents Fund and other campus annual giving funds. These gifts had an immediate impact by providing critical support for areas of greatest need, including student-advising services, small-course offerings, campus-safety programs, classroom technology and upgrades, and the retention of Berkeley's top faculty. </span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody">  We invite you to join our community of donors to The Cal Parents Fund. Your gift is an important investment in your student and UC Berkeley. Please support the 2012-13 Cal Parents Fund today. </span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody"><a href="howto.shtml">How to Make a 
          Gift</a></span></p>
		   <p><span class="smallbody"><a href="http://givetocal.berkeley.edu/fund/?f=FX0120000">Make a 
          Gift Online</a></span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody"><a href="/gifts/parentsfund.shtml">About The 
          Cal Parents Fund</a> </span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody"><a href="/gifts/benefit.shtml">How The Cal Parents 
          Fund Benefits Berkeley Students</a></span></p>
        <p><span class="smallbody"><a href="pfundboard.shtml">The Cal Parents  Board - Meet the Volunteers <br>
        </a></span></p>
      </div>
      <!-- closing div for class="hilite" -->
