          <h6>Take Part in Cal Advocacy</h6>
          <p>Legislators make decisions that can strengthen &#8212; or weaken 
            &#8212; UC Berkeley's ability to educate students, contribute cutting-edge 
            research, and continue as a vital driver of California's economy. 
            Make your support for Cal known in Sacramento and Washington, D.C. 
